divs: Sighting DetailsOn the cloudy days.... I was outside and happen to look up into the sky... The ship that I saw was covered or hidden with the clouds and see-thru. when it started to move slowly i could see the flat smooth shape in the puffy clouds. then it disappeared. hidden by the clouds again.
